59:19.305 --> 59:20.847
Who is he?

59:20.932 --> 59:23.433
He's connected to the guys
who hired me.

59:23.518 --> 59:25.769
- I don't get it.
- You destroyed my workups.

59:25.853 --> 59:27.396
Number four's due.
What'd you think, night's over?

59:27.480 --> 59:29.523
Called on account of rain?

59:29.607 --> 59:31.817
You go in there, say you're me.
Score the backups.

59:31.901 --> 59:34.069
They'll be on flash drive or CD.

59:34.153 --> 59:36.154
- Me? How come you don't go?
- I don't meet people.

59:36.239 --> 59:37.823
Risk management. Anonymity.
I protect mine.

59:37.907 --> 59:39.324
You're not gonna screw that up.

59:39.409 --> 59:42.452
I got a contract with their bosses.
These guys don't get to meet me.

59:42.537 --> 59:45.038
They don't know what I look like.

59:46.624 --> 59:49.251
If I don't pull it off, then...

59:49.335 --> 59:51.837
They will kill you.
Now, you got 10 minutes.

59:51.921 --> 59:53.589
At 10:01, I drive to the hospital

59:53.673 --> 59:55.591
